quran[5]{c,v,t}:
  2,177,neki yahi nahi ke tum mashriq ya maghrib ko ( qibla samajh kar un ) ki taraf munh karlo balkay neki yeh hai ke log khuda par aur roz akhirat par aur firshton par aur ( khuda ki ) kitaab par aur payghambaroon par imaan layein. aur maal bawajood Aziz rakhnay ke rishta daaron aur yatimon aur mohtajon aur musafiron aur mangnay walon ko den aur gardnon ( ke chhuranay ) mein ( kharch karen ) aur namaz parheen aur zakaat den. aur jab ehad karlen to is ko poora karen. aur sakhti aur takleef mein aur ( maarka ) kaarzar ke waqt saabit qadam rahen. yahi log hain jo ( imaan mein ) sachey hain aur yahi hain jo ( khuda se ) darny walay hain
  2,178,momino! tum ko mqtolon ke baray mein qisaas ( yani khoon ke badlay khoon ) ka hukum diya jata hai ( is terhan par ke ) azad ke badlay azad ( mara jaye ) aur ghulam ke badlay ghulam aur aurat ke badlay aurat aur qaatil ko is ke ( maqtool ) bhai ( ke qisaas mein ) se kuch maaf kardiya jaye to ( waris maqtool ) ko pasandeeda tareeq se ( qarar daad ki ) pairwi ( yani مطالبہٴ khoon baha ) karna aur ( qaatil ko ) khush khoi ke sath ada karna chahiye yeh perwar-digaar ki taraf se tumahray liye aasani aur meharbani hai jo is ke baad zayad-ti kere is ke liye dukh ka azaab hai
  2,179,aur ae ahal aqal ( hukum ) qisaas mein ( tumhari ) zindagani hai ke tum ( qatal o khonrizi se ) bachcho
  2,180,tum par farzkiya jata hai ke jab tum mein se kisi ko mout ka waqt aajay to agar woh kuch maal chore jaane wala ho to maa ba p aur rishta daaron ke liye dastoor ke mutabiq wasiyat krjaye ( khuda se ) dar ne walon par yeh aik haq hai
  2,181,jo shakhs wasiyat ko suneney ke baad badal daaley to is ( ke badalny ) ka gunah inhen logon par hai jo is ko badleen. aur be shak khuda santa jaanta hai
